headline: Equifax Q2 Earnings & Revenues Surpass Estimates, Increase Y/Y
summary: EFX posts strong second-quarter 2025 results, with earnings up 9.9% and revenues climbing 7.7%, prompting raised outlooks for the third quarter and 2025.
